\section{Heavy by design}{

This function performs \code{sim_reps} refits of the model. Each refit
uses the same engine path as the original fit (TMB Laplace
approximation) and so inherits the same per-fit cost. Wrap calls
in \code{system.time()} to budget realistically before scaling
\code{sim_reps} upward.
